'''Ooglata''' was a creature native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ithor/Legends|Ithor]]; they were as a food source. Their [[Egg/Legends|eggs]] were best served scrambled. The dining establishment, [[BanthaQuik!]], used these eggs in one of their popular dishes, [[Ithor Delight]].<ref name="DH">{{JournalCite|9|Death-Hunter}}</ref>

